verbose_text: For example, CD4 + FOXP3 + intratumoral Treg cells were shown to suppress cetuximab mediated ADCC (antibody dependent cellular cytotoxicity) and were correlated with poor clinical outcome in two prospective clinical trial cohorts XREF_BIBR.
